1135:**Generated matrix format (canonical, from matrix-merger):**
1136:
1137:```markdown
1138:# Goal Coverage Matrix — Phase {phase}
1139:**Generated:** {ISO-timestamp}
1140:**Source:** RUNTIME-MAP.json + .surface-probe-results.json + LIFECYCLE-SPECS.json + TEST-FIXTURE-DAG.json + TEST-EXECUTION-PLAN.json
1141:**Merger:** _shared/lib/matrix-merger.sh v2.65.1
1142:**Lifecycle contracts consumed:** {N} goal(s); fixture nodes={N}; deep_specs_present={true|false}
1143:
1144:## Summary
1145:- Total goals: {N}
1146:- READY: {N}
1147:- BLOCKED: {N}
1148:- NOT_SCANNED: {N} (intermediate)
1149:- UNREACHABLE: {N}
1150:- INFRA_PENDING: {N}
1151:- FAILED: {N} (intermediate)
1152:
1153:## By Priority
1154:| Priority | Ready | Blocked | Other | Total | Threshold | Pass % | Status |
1155:|----------|-------|---------|-------|-------|-----------|--------|--------|
1156:| critical | {N} | {N} | {N} | {N} | 100% | {X%} | ✅ PASS/⛔ BLOCK |
1157:| important | {N} | {N} | {N} | {N} | 80% | {X%} | ... |
1158:| nice-to-have | {N} | {N} | {N} | {N} | 50% | {X%} | ... |
1159:
1160:## Goal Details
1161:| Goal | Priority | Surface | Status | Evidence |
1162:|------|----------|---------|--------|----------|
1163:| G-01 | critical | api | READY | handler=apps/api/src/... |
1164:
1165:## Gate: ✅/⛔/⚠️ {VERDICT}
1166:{PASS|BLOCK|INTERMEDIATE message with next-action hints}
1167:```
1168:
1169:### 4d: Inline triage + apply scope-tag actions (v1.14.0+ A.2)
1170:
1171:Triage chạy **inline** ngay sau matrix ghi, TRƯỚC 100% gate. Mục đích: đọc scope tag (`depends_on_phase`, `verification_strategy`) từ CONTEXT.md, phân loại mỗi UNREACHABLE thành verdict + action_required, rồi áp dụng action nào autonomous được (mark_deferred/mark_manual). Các action cần người quyết định (spawn_fix_agent, draft_amendment_ask, prompt_scope_tag) sẽ ghi vào hàng đợi nhưng vẫn BLOCK gate — **không có đường thoát ngụỵ trang**.
1172:
1173:```bash
1174:session_mark_step "4d-inline-triage"
1175:echo ""
1176:echo "🔍 Triage + áp dụng action cho UNREACHABLE goals (v1.14.0+)..."
1177:
1178:# v1.14.3 H3 — pre-scan test source for @deferred markers so triage sees them
1179:# alongside scope tags. Fixes gap where executor-written it.skip('@deferred X')
1180:# was ignored (tests were skipped but matrix still BLOCKED).
1181:DEFER_SCANNER="${VG_SCRIPT_ROOT:-${VG_HOME:-$HOME/.vgflow}/scripts}/scan-deferred-tests.py"
1182:if [ -f "$DEFER_SCANNER" ]; then
1183:  echo "▸ Pre-scan: @deferred markers in test source..."
1184:  ${PYTHON_BIN:-python3} "$DEFER_SCANNER" \
1185:    --phase-dir "${PHASE_DIR}" --repo-root "${REPO_ROOT:-.}" 2>&1 | tail -12 || true
1186:  # Writes .deferred-tests.json — consumed by unreachable-triage below
1187:fi
1188:
1189:# Chạy triage (sinh .unreachable-triage.json + UNREACHABLE-TRIAGE.md)
1190:source "${VG_COMMAND_ROOT:-${VG_HOME:-$HOME/.vgflow}/commands/vg}/_shared/lib/unreachable-triage.sh" 2>/dev/null || true
1191:if type -t triage_unreachable_goals >/dev/null 2>&1; then
1192:  triage_unreachable_goals "$PHASE_DIR" "$PHASE_NUMBER"
1193:else
1194:  echo "⚠ unreachable-triage.sh missing — triage bị bỏ qua, 100% gate sẽ hard-block mọi UNREACHABLE." >&2
1195:fi
1196:
1197:TRIAGE_JSON="${PHASE_DIR}/.unreachable-triage.json"
1198:MATRIX="${PHASE_DIR}/GOAL-COVERAGE-MATRIX.md"
1199:
1200:if [ -f "$TRIAGE_JSON" ] && [ -f "$MATRIX" ]; then
1201:  # Áp dụng action_required autonomous: mark_deferred, mark_manual
1202:  # Những action còn lại (spawn_fix_agent, draft_amendment_ask, prompt_scope_tag) ghi log + để BLOCK.
1203:  PYTHONIOENCODING=utf-8 ${PYTHON_BIN} - "$TRIAGE_JSON" "$MATRIX" "$PHASE_DIR" "$PHASE_NUMBER" <<'PY'
1204:import json, sys, re
1205:from pathlib import Path
1206:from datetime import datetime, timezone
1207:
1208:triage_path = Path(sys.argv[1])
1209:matrix_path = Path(sys.argv[2])
1210:phase_dir   = Path(sys.argv[3])
1211:phase_num   = sys.argv[4]
1212:
1213:try:
1214:    triage = json.loads(triage_path.read_text(encoding="utf-8"))
1215:except Exception as e:
1216:    print(f"⚠ Không đọc được triage JSON: {e}")
1217:    sys.exit(0)
1218:
1219:verdicts = triage.get("verdicts", {})
1220:
1221:# v1.14.3 H3 — merge .deferred-tests.json as additional deferral source
1222:# (test files with it.skip('@deferred X') markers that aren't in CONTEXT.md scope tags).
1223:deferred_tests_path = phase_dir / ".deferred-tests.json"
1224:test_deferrals = {}  # ts_id → {reason, kind}
1225:if deferred_tests_path.exists():
1226:    try:
1227:        dt = json.loads(deferred_tests_path.read_text(encoding="utf-8"))
1228:        for entry in dt.get("deferred_tests", []):
1229:            ts = entry.get("ts_id")
1230:            if ts:
1231:                test_deferrals[ts] = entry
1232:    except Exception as e:
1233:        print(f"⚠ Không đọc được .deferred-tests.json: {e}")
1234:
1235:if not verdicts and not test_deferrals:
1236:    print("ℹ Không có UNREACHABLE cần triage — skip.")
1237:    sys.exit(0)
1238:
1239:matrix_text = matrix_path.read_text(encoding="utf-8")
1240:pending_queue = []   # cho các action chờ user / destructive
1241:applied       = {"mark_deferred": [], "mark_manual": [], "pending": []}
1242:
1243:def update_status_in_matrix(text, gid, new_status, note=""):
1244:    # Tìm dòng trong ## Goal Details có `| G-XX | ... | UNREACHABLE | ... |`
1245:    # Thay UNREACHABLE → new_status; append note vào evidence nếu có.
1246:    pat = re.compile(r'^(\| *' + re.escape(gid) + r' *\|[^|]*\|[^|]*\|) *UNREACHABLE *(\|[^\n]*)', re.M)
1247:    def _repl(m):
1248:        prefix = m.group(1)
1249:        suffix = m.group(2)
1250:        if note:
1251:            suffix = suffix.rstrip("|").rstrip() + f" ({note})|"
1252:        return f"{prefix} {new_status} {suffix}"
1253:    return pat.sub(_repl, text, count=1)
1254:
1255:for gid, v in verdicts.items():
1256:    action   = v.get("action_required")
1257:    params   = v.get("action_params", {})
1258:    verdict  = v.get("verdict", "")
1259:
1260:    if action == "mark_deferred":
1261:        target = params.get("target_phase", "?")
1262:        matrix_text = update_status_in_matrix(matrix_text, gid, "DEFERRED", f"depends_on_phase: {target}")
1263:        applied["mark_deferred"].append((gid, target))
1264:    elif action == "mark_manual":
1265:        strat = params.get("strategy", "manual")
1266:        matrix_text = update_status_in_matrix(matrix_text, gid, "MANUAL", f"verification: {strat}")
1267:        applied["mark_manual"].append((gid, strat))
1268:    elif action in ("spawn_fix_agent", "draft_amendment_ask", "prompt_scope_tag"):
1269:        # Giữ UNREACHABLE — gate sẽ block; ghi vào pending queue
1270:        pending_queue.append({
1271:            "phase":   phase_num,
1272:            "goal_id": gid,
1273:            "verdict": verdict,
1274:            "action":  action,
1275:            "params":  params,
1276:            "title":   v.get("title", "(no title)"),
1277:            "queued_at": datetime.now(timezone.utc).isoformat(),
1278:        })
1279:        applied["pending"].append((gid, action))
1280:
1281:# v1.14.3 H3 — apply test-level deferrals (fills gap where scope tags missing
1282:# but test source has it.skip('@deferred X')). Status depends on defer_kind:
1283:#   depends_on_phase + test-codegen → DEFERRED
1284:#   manual + faketime               → MANUAL
1285:#   unknown                         → log as pending, leave as UNREACHABLE
1286:for ts_id, entry in test_deferrals.items():
1287:    # ts_id is "TS-XX"; matrix may have goal_ids like "TS-16" or "G-XX" — try TS- first
1288:    gid = ts_id
1289:    kind = entry.get("defer_kind", "unknown")
1290:    reason = entry.get("defer_reason", "")
1291:    if kind in ("depends_on_phase", "test-codegen"):
1292:        matrix_text = update_status_in_matrix(
1293:            matrix_text, gid, "DEFERRED",
1294:            f"test.skip @deferred: {reason[:50]}",
1295:        )
1296:        applied["mark_deferred"].append((gid, f"test-marker:{kind}"))
1297:    elif kind in ("manual", "faketime"):
1298:        matrix_text = update_status_in_matrix(
1299:            matrix_text, gid, "MANUAL",
1300:            f"test.skip @deferred: {reason[:50]}",
1301:        )
1302:        applied["mark_manual"].append((gid, kind))
1303:    else:
1304:        pending_queue.append({
1305:            "phase":   phase_num,
1306:            "goal_id": gid,
1307:            "verdict": "test-level @deferred with unknown kind",
1308:            "action":  "review_test_defer_reason",
1309:            "params":  {"reason": reason, "source": entry.get("source_file", "")},
1310:            "title":   entry.get("test_title", ""),
1311:            "queued_at": datetime.now(timezone.utc).isoformat(),
1312:        })
1313:        applied["pending"].append((gid, "test-defer-unknown"))
1314:
1315:# Re-sync header counts trong "## Summary" block nếu có thay đổi
1316:def recount_summary(text):
1317:    details = re.search(r'^## Goal Details\s*\n(.*?)(?=^\s*## |\Z)', text, re.M|re.S)
1318:    if not details:
1319:        return text
1320:    body = details.group(1)
1321:    counts = {"READY":0, "BLOCKED":0, "UNREACHABLE":0, "INFRA_PENDING":0,
1322:              "DEFERRED":0, "MANUAL":0, "NOT_SCANNED":0, "FAILED":0}
1323:    for line in body.splitlines():
1324:        for k in counts:
1325:            # Status cell đứng giữa 2 dấu | — tránh match keyword trong evidence
1326:            if re.search(r'\|\s*' + k + r'\s*\|', line):
1327:                counts[k] += 1
1328:                break
1329:    def _rewrite_summary(m):
1330:        total = sum(counts.values())
1331:        new = [
1332:            "## Summary",
1333:            f"- Total goals: {total}",
1334:            f"- READY: {counts['READY']}",
1335:            f"- DEFERRED: {counts['DEFERRED']} (tagged depends_on_phase)",
1336:            f"- MANUAL: {counts['MANUAL']} (tagged verification_strategy)",
1337:            f"- BLOCKED: {counts['BLOCKED']}",
1338:            f"- UNREACHABLE: {counts['UNREACHABLE']}",
1339:            f"- INFRA_PENDING: {counts['INFRA_PENDING']}",
1340:            f"- NOT_SCANNED: {counts['NOT_SCANNED']} (intermediate)",
1341:            f"- FAILED: {counts['FAILED']} (intermediate)",
1342:            ""
1343:        ]
1344:        return "\n".join(new)
1345:    new_text = re.sub(r'^## Summary\n(?:[-*].*\n)+', _rewrite_summary, text, count=1, flags=re.M)
1346:    return new_text
1347:
1348:matrix_text = recount_summary(matrix_text)
1349:matrix_path.write_text(matrix_text, encoding="utf-8")
1350:
1351:# Ghi pending queue vào .vg/PENDING-USER-REVIEW.md (append-only)
1352:if pending_queue:
1353:    pending_file = Path(".vg/PENDING-USER-REVIEW.md")
1354:    pending_file.parent.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)
1355:    header_needed = not pending_file.exists()
1356:    with pending_file.open("a", encoding="utf-8") as f:
1357:        if header_needed:
1358:            f.write("# Pending user review — hàng đợi quyết định đang chờ\n\n")
1359:            f.write("Mỗi mục là một goal cần quyết định (scope tag / fix / amendment). ")
1360:            f.write("User review xong → duyệt queue thay vì bị hỏi từng cái.\n\n")
1361:            f.write("| Phase | Goal | Verdict | Action cần | Tiêu đề | Queued at |\n")
1362:            f.write("|---|---|---|---|---|---|\n")
1363:        for p in pending_queue:
1364:            f.write(f"| {p['phase']} | {p['goal_id']} | {p['verdict']} | {p['action']} | "
1365:                    f"{p['title'][:60]} | {p['queued_at']} |\n")
1366:
1367:# Narration
1368:print(f"▸ Triage applied: "
1369:      f"{len(applied['mark_deferred'])} → DEFERRED, "
1370:      f"{len(applied['mark_manual'])} → MANUAL, "
1371:      f"{len(applied['pending'])} → chờ người duyệt")
1372:for gid, tgt in applied["mark_deferred"]:
1373:    print(f"  🔁 {gid} → DEFERRED (depends_on_phase: {tgt})")
1374:for gid, strat in applied["mark_manual"]:
1375:    print(f"  ✋ {gid} → MANUAL ({strat})")
1376:for gid, act in applied["pending"]:
1377:    print(f"  ⏳ {gid} → {act} (giữ UNREACHABLE, gate sẽ BLOCK đến khi giải quyết)")
1378:PY
1379:else
1380:  [ -f "$TRIAGE_JSON" ] || echo "ℹ Không có triage JSON (không UNREACHABLE goal nào) — skip apply."
1381:fi
