621:    "read_after_update": "Re-read from a clean context and assert updated fields, derived state, events, permissions, or view state.",
622:    "delete": "Cleanup by delete, revoke, cancel, deactivate, rollback fixture, or restore original view/config state.",
623:    "read_after_delete": "Re-read active list/detail and assert no active test-owned resource remains; audit row may remain if required.",
