644:### Output consumed by review
645:
646:`${PHASE_DIR}/TEST-SPEC-CROSSAI.md` — review preflight (already reads diagnostic surface per PR #183) extended to surface CrossAI verdict + findings count in `GOAL-COVERAGE-MATRIX.md` provenance.
