792:<step name="4_self_review">
793:
794:## Step 4.5: codegen self-review (`4_self_review`)
795:
796:After codegen, verify generated `.spec.ts` files compile via `npx playwright --list`. Catch syntax errors before `/vg:test` Step 2 execute time.
797:
798:**Run check:**
799:
800:```bash
801:SELF_REVIEW_LOG="${PHASE_DIR}/.step-markers/test-spec/4_self_review.log"
802:mkdir -p "$(dirname "$SELF_REVIEW_LOG")"
803:
804:RETRY=0
805:MAX_RETRY=2
806:while [ $RETRY -le $MAX_RETRY ]; do
807:  if npx playwright --list tests/e2e/lifecycle/ > "$SELF_REVIEW_LOG" 2>&1; then
808:    echo "✓ Codegen self-review PASS (retry=$RETRY)"
809:    break
810:  fi
811:  RETRY=$((RETRY + 1))
812:  if [ $RETRY -gt $MAX_RETRY ]; then
813:    echo "⛔ Codegen self-review FAIL after $MAX_RETRY retries — see $SELF_REVIEW_LOG"
814:    echo "Escalate to user. Manual fix or rollback codegen."
815:    exit 1
816:  fi
817:  echo "⚠ Self-review FAIL (retry=$RETRY) — re-running codegen subagent"
818:  # Re-spawn vg-test-codegen with prior output context
819:done
820:
821:"${PYTHON_BIN:-python3}" "$ORCH" mark-step test-spec 4_self_review 2>/dev/null || true
822:```
