1696:317:**Per-goal runtime rule (enforced in step 5c_goal_verification):**
1697:318:- `status == READY` + `goal_sequence.steps[]` ≥ 1 → replay (normal path)
1698:319:- `status == UNREACHABLE|INFRA_PENDING` → skip với log "expected skip" (không fail, không count)
