1707:328:## STEP 1.4 — telemetry suggestions + emit-tasklist (0c_telemetry_suggestions + create_task_tracker)
1708:329:
1709:330:### 1.4a — Reactive telemetry suggestions (0c_telemetry_suggestions)
1710:331:
1711:332:Read telemetry suggestions and surface to user. Security validators
1712:333:(UNQUARANTINABLE) are NEVER suggested for skip, regardless of pass rate.
1713:334:
1714:335:```bash
1715:336:vg-orchestrator step-active 0c_telemetry_suggestions
1716:337:
1717:338:if [ -x "$(command -v ${PYTHON_BIN:-python3})" ] && [ -f ".claude/scripts/telemetry-suggest.py" ]; then
1718:339:  SUGGESTIONS=$(${PYTHON_BIN:-python3} .claude/scripts/telemetry-suggest.py --command vg:test 2>/dev/null || echo "")
1719:340:  if [ -n "$SUGGESTIONS" ]; then
1720:341:    COUNT=$(echo "$SUGGESTIONS" | grep -c '^{' || echo 0)
1721:342:    if [ "${COUNT:-0}" -gt 0 ]; then
1722:343:      echo "▸ Telemetry suggestions for vg:test (${COUNT}, advisory):"
1723:344:      echo "$SUGGESTIONS" | head -5 | ${PYTHON_BIN:-python3} -c "
1724:345:import json, sys
1725:346:for line in sys.stdin:
1726:347:    line=line.strip()
1727:348:    if not line: continue
