2079:224:
2080:225:Prompt body (rendered into `${PROMPT_FILE}` for Codex, or passed inline to
2081:226:the `Agent(...)` tool call on Claude):
2082:227:
2083:228:```
2084:229:Agent(
2085:230:  model="$SPAWN_MODEL",
2086:231:  description="[fix ${idx}/${total}] ${severity} ${file}:${line} — ${bug_type}"
2087:232:):
2088:233:  prompt = """
