2096:241:  File hint: ${suspected_file}
2097:242:  Evidence: ${console_errors}, ${network_failures}, ${screenshot}
2098:243:
2099:244:  ## CONSTRAINTS
2100:245:  - Touch only files related to this bug
2101:246:  - No refactor/rename unless required for fix
2102:247:  - Write test if missing (project convention)
2103:248:  - Commit: fix(${phase}): ${short description}
2104:249:  - Per CONTEXT.md D-XX OR Covers goal: G-XX in commit body
2105:250:
2106:251:  ## RETURN
