3010:1155:|----------|-------|---------|-------|-------|-----------|--------|--------|
3011:1156:| critical | {N} | {N} | {N} | {N} | 100% | {X%} | ✅ PASS/⛔ BLOCK |
3012:1157:| important | {N} | {N} | {N} | {N} | 80% | {X%} | ... |
3013:1158:| nice-to-have | {N} | {N} | {N} | {N} | 50% | {X%} | ... |
