3546:137:
3547:138:OR inlines the array if the spec file lives outside the import tree.
3548:139:DO NOT regex-parse the markdown table — VARIANTS.json is authoritative
3549:140:and validated by verify-variants-json.py.
3550:141:</seed_contract>
