5257:452:## Example — real goal (phase 14 G-01)
5258:453:
5259:454:```yaml
5260:455:---
5261:456:id: G-01
5262:457:title: "Publisher login respects domain-role fit"
5263:458:priority: critical
5264:459:surface: api + ui
5265:460:actor: publisher (role=publisher, unauthenticated before login)
5266:461:precondition:
5267:462:  - has_verified_account
5268:463:  - domain_route_configured (ssp.vollx.com → publisher app)
5269:464:trigger: "POST /api/v1/auth/login from ssp.vollx.com origin"
5270:465:main_steps:
5271:466:  - S1: Client POST credentials + domain header to /api/v1/auth/login
5272:467:  - S2: API validates domain-role fit via AuthDomain enum
5273:468:  - S3: API issues JWT with domain=ssp claim + refresh cookie scoped to ssp domain
5274:469:  - S4: Client redirected to publisher dashboard
5275:470:  - S5: Subsequent requests include JWT — middleware validates JWT.domain matches Origin header
5276:471:alternate_flows:
5277:472:  - name: domain_role_mismatch
5278:473:    trigger: admin account attempts login from ssp.vollx.com
5279:474:    expected: 403 with VG_ERR_DOMAIN_ROLE_UNFIT + Vietnamese toast "Tài khoản không có quyền cho domain này"
5280:475:  - name: invalid_origin
5281:476:    trigger: request from unapproved domain (e.g. evil.com)
5282:477:    expected: 403 via CORS preflight + VG_ERR_DOMAIN_ORIGIN_INVALID logged
5283:478:postcondition:
5284:479:  - jwt_issued with domain=ssp in payload
5285:480:  - refresh_cookie set with Domain=.ssp.vollx.com Path=/api/v1/auth
5286:481:  - session row in Redis with key "session:ssp:{user_id}:{device_id}"
5287:482:  - event "auth.login" emitted with {domain, user_id, success: true}
5288:483:verification: automated
5289:484:tests: [TS-01, TS-02]
5290:485:status: READY
5291:486:evidence_file: apps/web/e2e/auth-domain-isolation.spec.ts:23
5292:487:---
5293:488:
5294:489:Publisher can only log in from their designated SSP domain. Cross-domain
5295:490:attempts (admin credentials on SSP domain) are rejected with clear error
5296:491:message in Vietnamese. Session cookies scoped to domain prevent cross-
5297:492:site token leak.
5298:493:```
