5300:495:## Migration
5301:496:
5302:497:- **Existing goals** (v1.14 format): no action needed. Missing fields = validators skip enrichment checks.
5303:498:- **New phases** (scope/blueprint v2+): blueprint step 2b5 SHOULD emit enriched format. AI reads this template to infer structure.
5304:499:- **Manual enrichment**: user edits TEST-GOALS.md adding fields. Validators re-run, may unlock additional coverage.
5305:500:
5306:501:## Consumer behavior
5307:502:
5308:503:| Command | Reads enriched fields | Effect |
5309:504:|---------|----------------------|--------|
5310:505:| `/vg:blueprint` step 2b5 | Generates via AI prompt | AI pattern-matches template → uses enriched format |
5311:506:| `/vg:build` executor | Reads `precondition` + `alternate_flows` | Task context includes error handling requirements |
5312:507:| `/vg:review` goal comparison | Reads `main_steps` + `postcondition` | Maps to RUNTIME-MAP observed sequences |
5313:508:| `/vg:test` codegen | Reads all enriched fields | Generates Playwright scenarios per `alternate_flows` names |
5314:509:| `/vg:accept` UAT checklist | Reads `actor` + `postcondition` | User UAT items phrased in enriched language |
