5326:1:#!/usr/bin/env python3
5327:2:"""Generate closed-loop lifecycle specs from existing phase artifacts.
5328:3:
5329:4:This is the deterministic counterpart to the lifecycle-depth gate. It turns
5330:5:TEST-GOALS, API hints, and phase docs into a LIFECYCLE-SPECS.json contract that
