10430:651:## Step 4: codegen (`4_codegen`)
10431:652:
10432:653:Spawn `vg-test-codegen` subagent to generate Playwright lifecycle specs per goal. Smart-routing applies lens set per `goal_type` from `GOAL-COVERAGE-MATRIX.json`.
10433:654:
10434:655:**Smart-routing lens map:**
10435:656:
10436:657:| `goal_type` | Lens set |
10437:658:|---|---|
10438:659:| `mutation` | `idor` + `mass-assignment` + `authz-negative` + `business-logic` |
10439:660:| `read` | `authz` + `info-disclosure` + `tenant-boundary` |
10440:661:| `auth` | `auth-jwt` + `csrf` + `duplicate-submit` |
10441:662:| `default` | `business-coherence` + `input-injection` |
10442:663:
10443:664:**Subagent invocation:**
10444:665:
10445:666:Read `commands/vg/_shared/test/codegen/delegation.md` and `commands/vg/_shared/test/codegen/overview.md` (existing files, no change). Then:
10446:667:
10447:668:```
10448:669:Agent(
10449:670:  subagent_type="vg-test-codegen",
10450:671:  prompt=<from delegation.md template>,
10451:672:  input={
10452:673:    phase_dir: "${PHASE_DIR}",
10453:674:    phase_number: "${PHASE_NUMBER}",
10454:675:    phase_profile: "${PHASE_PROFILE}",
10455:676:    runtime_map_path: "${PHASE_DIR}/RUNTIME-MAP.json",
10456:677:    goal_coverage_matrix_path: "${PHASE_DIR}/GOAL-COVERAGE-MATRIX.json",
10457:678:    generated_tests_dir: "tests/e2e/lifecycle/",
10458:679:    lens_routing_map: <smart-routing map above>
10459:680:  }
10460:681:)
10461:682:```
